name: Office Work Purple Frame
description:
"Working at that particular company in the late 80s was one of the worst things I've ever done, every day was a bore and the only thing I could think about was why every day I was wasting my life there."

Office Work Purple Frame initially limited to 8, all of which will be given away with a purchase of Handheld Game Collection Gold Frame. All editions not collected within 24 hours of announcement will be burned.
